<title type="html"><![CDATA[Quran &amp; its Sciences • &quot;Between every two calls of Prayer (Adhān and Iqāmah)...]]></title>

<category term="Quran &amp; its Sciences" scheme="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewforum.php?f=6" label="Quran &amp; its Sciences"/>
<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=1224&amp;p=1290#p1290"><![CDATA[
The Messenger of Allāh صلى الله عليه وسلم said:<br /><br />&quot;Between every two calls of Prayer (Adhān and Iqāmah)[quote][/quote] there is a Salah; between every two calls there is a Salah&quot;. In the third time he صلى الله عليه وسلم added: 'For whoever wishes to do so'&quot;.<br /><br />Agreed Upon<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=63">Abu Faatimah</a> — Sun Mar 05, 2017 1:30 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
